snippet.title: Rogue Door Defense [Trailer] - Tower Defense Mazing Game 2022
snippet.description:
Rogue Door Defense is a tower defense mazing game with rouge-lite elements. Choose a door, defeat the enemies behind it and claim your unique reward. Build and upgrade different towers. Design your own maze to defend your lives against the attacking waves of monsters and powerful bosses.

Get it on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1959880/Rogue_Door_Defense/
